title: Delay Your Gratification
itunes:title: Delay Your Gratification
description:
Episode 153 - People overestimate what they can do in a year but underestimate what they can do in a decade. Why are most people unsuccessful? Because they want instant gratification - sleeping in, Netflix, eating junk food.  But success if found in delayed gratification - working hard now and getting the results later. In this episode I dive into this topic and talk about how to set yourself up for success in the future.
